  "title": "Excavator Operator",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Operate the excavator safely at Waste Management Company, indoor environment</li><li>Coordinate with supervisor and team members</li><li>Perform daily routine checks and maintain the excavator in good condition</li><li>Always comply with the authorities' rules and regulations</li><li>Perform other adhoc duties assigned by superior</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Must possessed valid Registered Excavator Operator (REO) license</li><li>Physically fit</li><li>Minimum 2 year experience in operating excavator</li><li>Team Player and able to work independently with positive work attitude</li></ul>",
